name: awardmanagementWyoming
0:
”Alexa, open award management wyoming”
”Alexa, ask award management wyoming to find Mobility info.”
”Alexa, ask award management wyoming to search for Mobility.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: award management wyoming
des: The skill allows you to check whether a company is registered in system for award management system (http://www.sam.gov) as Wyoming's state company, and if registered, get a DUNS number. By default we search any business name that contains specified word, so if you say "Mobility", then all companies containing the word 'Mobility' in their name will be returned as a result, for example, "Medic Mobility" and "Mobility Trade House".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
